&gt; Not calling glEnable(GL_BLEND) in initGL but calling glEnable(GL_BLEND) when you draw the text should make it work.

    glEnable(GL_BLEND);
    font.drawString(0, 0, &quot;This is a text that should appear&quot;);
    glDisable(GL_BLEND);

